>> description: Spaghetti with tomato, onion and egg
>> servings: 1

Cook @spaghetti{100%g} in #pot with @salt.

Chop @tomato{1%pc} and @onion{1%pc}

Fry onion for ~onion{4%min} in #pan

Add tomato to pan and fry for another ~tomato{4%min}

Beat @egg{1%pc}

Add spaghetti and egg to pan and fry another ~{3%min}

Remove from fire and add @basil
